{
  "stem": "2074.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then from the pigs, I crawled somewhere and I went on top of the attic, the same farm, to sit there, because I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If they're gonna kill me, they're going to kill me whatever it's gonna",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, I showed myself up for the guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came into the barn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he was a Nazi, but knowing my brother, he brought me something to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sit a while in his barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, the Nazi leaders were not afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To them, nobody was going to come look for a Jew, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so anyway, he brought me something to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The same day in the afternoon, he brings that girl that was with my brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother and my sister ran away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That girl couldn't keep up with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She left behind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was all full of blood so the farmer went to his farm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He found that girl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had a piece of glass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was cutting her wrist open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She wanted to die because she was left there laying in the fields.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was all full of blood and was still on the same farmer's farm.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he picked her up and cleaned up her hand and brought her upstairs to sit with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we sat there for quite a-- quite a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But see, I forgot to tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the beginning, right in the beginning, right after I washed myself up from the toilet, I went to a friend called [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Manka. ?] This is where I have on the film here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the film.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She's there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And with the pictures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "These are the people we went back to see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So her father was a Nazi leader.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
